text: Ekenäs Sport Club (abbreviated ESC) is a football club from Ekenäs, Raseborg in Finland. The club was formed in 2007 and their home ground is Ekenäs Centrumplan. The club is currently playing in the Kakkonen, the third tier of the Finnish league system. ==External links== *Official Website Category:Football clubs in Finland Category:Association football clubs established in 2007 Category:2007 establishments in Finland
